text.tspan: New tests for COVID-19 (7-day smoothed). For countries that don't report testing data on a daily basis, we
assume that testing changed equally on a daily basis over any periods in which no data was reported. This
produces a complete series of daily figures, which is then averaged over a rolling 7-day window.
Data source: Official data collated by Our World in Data (2022)
